T1  - The Production Administrative Structure: A Paradigm for Strategic Fit
AU  - Jelinek, Mariann
AU  - Burstein, Michael C.
Y1  - 1982/04/01
PY  - 1982
DA  - 1982/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1982.4285583
